Math-Random-MTwist
==================

PREREQUISITES

Perl >= 5.8
Test::More

mtwist needs a fairly "modern" C compiler (see IMPORANT NOTE in mtwist.h).


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


USAGE

See POD documentation in MTwist.pm


